-height:16px; }#meetup_oembed img { border:none; margin:0; padding:0; }#meetup_oembed a, #meetup_oembed a:visited, #meetup_oembed a:link { color: #1B76B3; text-decoration: none; cursor: hand; cursor: pointer; }#meetup_oembed a:hover { color: #1B76B3; text-decoration: underline; }#meetup_oembed a.mu_button { font-size:14px; -moz-border-radius:3px;-webkit-border-radius:3px;border-radius:3px;border:2px solid #A7241D;color:white!important;text-decoration:none;background-color: #CA3E47; background-image: -moz-linear-gradient(top, #ca3e47, #a8252e); background-image: -webkit-gradient(linear, left bottom, left top, color-stop(0, #a8252e), color-stop(1, #ca3e47));disvplay:inline-block;padding:5px 10px; }#meetup_oembed a.mu_button:hover { color: #fff!important; text-decoration: none; }#meetup_oembed .photo { width:50px; height:50px; overflow:hidden;background:#ccc;float:left;margin:0 5px 0 0;text-align:center;padding:1px; }#meetup_oembed .photo img { height:50px }#meetup_oembed .number { font-size:18px; }#meetup_oembed .thing { text-transform: uppercase; color: #555; }</style><div id=\"meetup_oembed\" style=\"height:302px\">     <div style=\"max-height:262px;overflow:hidden\">          <h3>Sài Gòn WordPress Meetup #26</h3>          <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px\">Thursday, Sep 20, 2018,  6:30 PM</p>          <p style=\"margin: 0 0 5px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Officience Vietnam</span><br /><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">16A Lê Hồng Phong, Phường 12, Quận 10 Thanh Pho Ho Chi Minh, VN</span></p>          <span style=\"color:#4F8A10;font-size:16px;\">71 WordPress Lovers Went</span>           <div style=\"margin:5px 0 10px\" class=\"mu_clearfix\">               <div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/c/d/f/c/thumb_280492732.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/a/3/c/e/thumb_280721934.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/2/f/6/8/thumb_280752136.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/1/0/8/2/thumb_270784226.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/c/a/7/d/thumb_280491837.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/c/6/2/5/thumb_280550725.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/5/2/b/d/thumb_280581181.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/7/9/d/d/thumb_276091197.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/8/b/b/0/thumb_255635760.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/6/6/0/c/thumb_280706124.jpeg\" /></div>          </div>          <p style=\"line-height:16px\">Vào ngày 20 tháng 9, chúng ta sẽ quay lại với Sài Gòn WordPress Meetup thứ 26 với một chủ đề hấp dẫn tất cả mọi người: SEO. Dù bạn làm site bán hàng, landing page, site tin tức thì bạn vẫn luôn cần SEO, hãy đến với meetup số 26 để cùng học hỏi và chia sẻ kinh nghiệm. Mọi người luôn có cái gì đó để chúng ta học hỏi. ## Chương trình <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/12.0.0-1/72x72/1f561.png\" alt=\"🕡\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> 18:30 đến 19:00&#8230;</p>     </div>     <p style=\"margin:10px 0 0;\"><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/Saigon-WordPress/events/254410283/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"mu_button\"><strong>Check out this Meetup &rarr;</strong></a></p></div>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Chương trình</h2>\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>Chúng ta luôn bắt đầu đúng giờ, vì vậy đừng bỏ lỡ một topic nào nhé.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Địa điểm</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Officience Vietnam : 16A Lê Hồng Phong, Phường 12, Quận 10</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/09/highres_466899254.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-684\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/09/highres_466899254.png 1098w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/09/highres_466899254-300x211.png 300w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/09/highres_466899254-768x539.png 768w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/09/highres_466899254-1024x719.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1098px) 100vw, 1098px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Tìm speaker</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Như bạn thấy, plan đã có nhưng chưa có speaker, vì vậy mong bạn cùng đóng góp bằng cách đăng ký chủ đề mà bạn muốn nói ở phần comment, hoặc gửi email về địa chỉ: nguyenvanduocit@gmail.com</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Tài trợ</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Xin cảm ơn:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Officience Vietnam đã luôn đồng hành và hỗ trợ địa điểm cho meetup.</li><li>Weglot đã hỗ trợ kinh phí cho thức ăn.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/06/IMG_4900.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-630\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/06/IMG_4900.jpg 3264w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/06/IMG_4900-300x225.jpg 300w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/06/IMG_4900-768x576.jpg 768w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/06/IMG_4900-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/06/IMG_4900-440x330.jpg 440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3264px) 100vw, 3264px\" /></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/06/IMG_4897.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-629\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/06/IMG_4897.jpg 3264w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/06/IMG_4897-300x225.jpg 300w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/06/IMG_4897-768x576.jpg 768w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/06/IMG_4897-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/06/IMG_4897-440x330.jpg 440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3264px) 100vw, 3264px\" /></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/fil