0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"shopify alternatives\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"shopify competitors\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=228833\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:601:\"<p>Are you looking for alternatives to Shopify? While Shopify is one of the most popular eCommerce solutions, there&#8217;re many other platforms you can use to create an online store. For the sake of your online business, you owe it to yourself to check all the best options on the market. In this article, we&#8217;ll share [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/shopify-competitors/\">12 Shopify Alternatives &#038; Competitors You Need to Try</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17156:\"<p>Are you looking for alternatives to Shopify? While Shopify is one of the most popular eCommerce solutions, there&#8217;re many other platforms you can use to create an online store. For the sake of your online business, you owe it to yourself to check all the best options on the market.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share the most popular alternatives to Shopify you can use.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WooCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. WooCommerce</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WooCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/woocommerce.png\" alt=\"WooCommerce\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228892\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/woocommerce.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/woocommerce-300x132.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/woocommerce-768x337.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WooCommerce is the most <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 BEST WordPress eCommerce Plugins Compared\">popular eCommerce platform</a> on the market. It comes as a plugin for WordPress which gives it a solid foundation. It can be used with additional WordPress plugins to add more features to your store.</p>\n<p>You can use the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-woocommerce-themes-online-store/\" title=\"50+ Best WooCommerce Themes for Your Online Store\">top WooCommerce themes</a> to design your shop. WooCommerce comes with integrations, payment methods, addons, and more. There&#8217;re multiple hosting companies that offer dedicated <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/woocommerce/\" title=\"Best WooCommerce Hosting [Speed Tests + Real Reviews]\">WooCommerce hosting</a> to provide what you need for a successful eCommerce site.</p>\n<p>If you run into a problem during the set up, then there&#8217;s a large WooCommerce community that&#8217;s ready to help you out. WooCommerce has the biggest market share in the eCommerce industry. You should also take a look at our expert&#8217;s review on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/shopify-vs-woocommerce/\" title=\"Shopify vs. WooCommerce – Which Is the Best eCommerce Platform\">Shopify vs WooCommerce</a> to see a side-by-side comparison between the 2 popular eCommerce platforms.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bigcommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"BigCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. BigCommerce</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bigcommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"BigCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bigcommerce.jpg\" alt=\"BigCommerce\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228864\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bigcommerce.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bigcommerce-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bigcommerce-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>BigCommerce is an excellent eCommerce solution to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-an-online-store-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Create an Online Store – Step by Step (with Pictures)\">start an online store</a>. It not only helps you build a shop, it also helps you get more orders by listing your products on Amazon, eBay, Facebook, and other popular networks.</p>\n<p>Trusted by millions of users, it&#8217;s a smart choice for small-to-large scale online businesses. BigCommerce allows you to choose a template, customize your website, accept payments, manage orders, and more. It helps you drive more traffic to your online store to improve your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-seo-tools-to-grow-your-site-traffic/\" title=\"9 Best SEO Tools to Grow Your Website Traffic, FAST!\">search engine rankings</a>.</p>\n<p>From getting an order to payments to shipping items to your customers, you&#8217;ll be covered by BigCommerce. It&#8217;s a hosted solution and gives Shopify some steep competition.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wix/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Wix\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Wix</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wix/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Wix\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/wix.png\" alt=\"Wix\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229900\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/wix.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/wix-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/wix-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Wix is a popular website building solution that can be used to create an online store. It&#8217;s a hosted solution, which means all you need much to start is their premium version. You can simply use the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\" title=\"7 Best Drag and Drop WordPress Page Builders Compared\">drag and drop builder</a> to add products, images, content, and set up your shop.</p>\n<p>It allows you to integrate payment methods like PayPal, authorize.net, and others to collect payments from clients. Wix has great documentation and you don&#8217;t need coding knowledge to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Make a Website - Step by Step (with Pictures)\">start a website</a> or online store.</p>\n<p>We also recommend you take a look at this complete <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wix-review/\" title=\"Wix Review – Is It Better than WordPress? [TESTED]\">Wix review</a>, so you can learn more about its features and functionalities.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/weebly/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Weebly\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. Weebly</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/weebly/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Weebly\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/weebly.png\" alt=\"Weebly\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229901\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/weebly.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/weebly-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/weebly-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Weebly is another simple, powerful <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-website-builders-for-beginners-compared/\" title=\"10 Best Website Builders for Beginners Compared\">website builder</a>. It can be used as an eCommerce platform to sell products online. Unlike other solutions, you can select your theme, change your fonts, add a background image, and more. It works with most of the popular payment methods to receive money from clients.</p>\n<p>You can start a free trial to get familiar with the platform, but their premium version is what you&#8217;ll need to set up a complete eCommerce shop. It has a drag and drop builder that can be used to easily add features to your site. Weebly can be an effective alternative to Shopify.</p>\n<p>For more information about the platform, you should check out our complete <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/weebly-review/\" title=\"Weebly Review – Is It the Best Choice for You?\">Weebly review</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://magento.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Magento\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. Magento</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://magento.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Magento\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/magento.jpg\" alt=\"Magento\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228867\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/magento.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/magento-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/magento-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Magento is one of the oldest and most popular eCommerce solutions in the world. It&#8217;s more difficult to set up than WooCommerce or any other solution listed in this article. The process to add products and images require tackling a steep learning curve.</p>\n<p>Other than that, Magento is a secure and highly regarded online shopping platform. It has a growing community that&#8217;s ready to help you work with Magento. It&#8217;s a self-hosted solution, which means you&#8217;ll need a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/difference-between-domain-name-and-web-hosting-revealed/\" title=\"What’s the Difference Between Domain Name and Web Hosting? (REVEALED)\">domain name and web hosting</a> to create your online store.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.squarespace.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Squarespace\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Squarespace</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.squarespace.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Squarespace\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/squarespace.png\" alt=\"Squarespace\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228868\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/squarespace.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/squarespace-300x132.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/squarespace-768x337.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Squarespace is a premium website builder and an <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-alternatives-popular-wordpress-competitors/\" title=\"WordPress Alternatives – 18 Popular WordPress Competitors\">alternative to WordPress</a>. It can be used to build eCommerce solutions with all the features you need. It includes custom templates, integrations, and a drag and drop builder to quickly set up your shopping site.</p>\n<p>For more information, you should also check out this article on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/squarespace-vs-wordpress-which-is-the-best-choice-expert-review/\" title=\"Squarespace vs. WordPress – Which is the Best Choice? (Expert Review)\">Squarespace vs WordPress</a>. It&#8217;s a hosted solution and you can start by signing up from their website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.3dcart.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"3dcart\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. 3dcart</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.3dcart.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"3dcart\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/3dcart.jpg\" alt=\"3dcart\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228869\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/3dcart.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/3dcart-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/3dcart-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>3dcart is a fully hosted eCommerce software that you can use to build your online store. It&#8217;s a premium solution and you need to pay monthly to keep your business alive. 3dcart has plans for single to multiple users. All their plans include no transaction fees, unlimited products capacity, customer support, 100+ payment solutions, and more.</p>\n<p>You can integrate your online store with Facebook, Stripe, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/mailchimp-for-wordpress/\" title=\"MailChimp for WordPress Review: Integrate MailChimp Into WordPress\">MailChimp</a>, Amazon.com, and other popular networks to get more conversions. It has ready-made themes to customize your store to your heart&#8217;s desire.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.zoey.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Zoey\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. Zoey</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.zoey.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Zoey\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/zoey.jpg\" alt=\"Zoey\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228871\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/zoey.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/zoey-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/zoey-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Zoey is an enterprise solution for B2B / wholesale eCommerce solutions. It&#8217;s a great choice for large scale businesses where customers can request a quote, talk with a salesperson, experience the product before purchasing, and more. With this online solution, you can avoid the paperwork and track every conversation in the backend of your store.</p>\n<p>It has <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-content-marketing-tools-plugins-wordpress/\" title=\"15 Best Content Marketing Tools and Plugins for WordPress\">website marketing tools</a> to grow your business with proper reporting, customer service, and more. Zoey has tons of themes and addons to customize your website. It&#8217;s flexible and easily integrates third-party solutions to meet your requirements.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.volusion.com/v1/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Volusion\" rel=\"nofollow\">9. Volusion</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.volusion.com/v1/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Volusion\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/volusion.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228873\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/volusion.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/volusion-300x132.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/volusion-768x337.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Volusion is a modern eCommerce and shopping cart software on the market. It has stunning themes to launch your shop and attract users. Volusion offers inventory management, unlimited products stock, easy payment solutions, marketing, and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-seo-tools-to-grow-your-site-traffic/\" title=\"9 Best SEO Tools to Grow Your Website Traffic, FAST!\">SEO tools</a>.</p>\n<p>Their customer support is well-known for helping with web designing, marketing, and brand publicity needs. Volusion is trusted by thousands of online stores to sell their products.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.pinnaclecart.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Pinnacle Cart\" rel=\"nofollow\">10. Pinnacle Cart</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.pinnaclecart.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Pinnacle Cart\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/pinnaclecart.jpg\" alt=\"Pinnacle Cart\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228889\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/pinnaclecart.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/pinnaclecart-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/pinnaclecart-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Pinnacle Cart is a popular webstore builder and eCommerce software. It has built-in custom templates, marketing tools, app integrations, and addons. It&#8217;s easy to set up and comes with online training from their experts.</p>\n<p>They offer <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/vps/\" title=\"VPS Hosting Reviews\">VPS hosting</a> and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/dedicated/\" title=\"Dedicated Server Hosting Reviews\">dedicated server hosting</a> of their own. Unlike many other shopping cart solutions, Pinnacle Cart has payment integrations with PayPal, Stripe, CardConnect, and more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.bigcartel.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Big Cartel\" rel=\"nofollow\">11. Big Cartel</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.bigcartel.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Big Cartel\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bigcartel.jpg\" alt=\"Big Cartel\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228890\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bigcartel.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bigcartel-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bigcartel-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Big Cartel is an eCommerce solution for artists and other creators. It comes with custom themes that can be used to sell paintings, t-shirts, prints, jewelry, and more. Using the free themes, you can customize the design and look of your online store.</p>\n<p>It has built-in tools to add products, manage orders, check stats, run promotions, publish ads, and more. It enables you to manage your online store from any device.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you learn about Shopify&#8217;s competitors. If you liked this article, then we also recommend you check out this guide on the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-blogging-platforms-beginners-compared/\" title=\"12 Best Blogging Platforms for Beginners Compared\">best blogging platforms for beginners</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/shopify-competitors/\">12 Shopify Alternatives &#038; Competitors You Need to Try</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"https://www.isitwp.com/shopify-competitors/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\