as multiple color schemes, custom widgets, colors, and typography for layouts.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/athemes-rocked-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Rocked Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\">16. Rocked Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/athemes-rocked-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Rocked Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/rockedpro.jpg\" alt=\"Rocked Pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229427\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/rockedpro.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/rockedpro-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/rockedpro-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Rocked Pro is a premium business theme for WordPress sites. It features a crelly slider, page templates, additional widgets, and more. The theme is compatible with Beaver Builder and other page builders which makes customization super easy. You can drag and drop your content and widgets to set up your site.</p>\n<p>It has support for WooCommerce to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-an-online-store-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Create an Online Store – Step by Step (with Pictures)\">make an eCommerce store</a>. The theme is translation-ready and works great for RTL languages. They have strong documentation and guides to fully explain the features included with the theme.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-struct/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Struct\" rel=\"nofollow\">17. Struct</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-struct/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Struct\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/struct.jpg\" alt=\"Struct\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229411\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/struct.jpg 77